{"tha-ap461:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap461:0.2":"Jagatidayakavagga ","tha-ap461:0.3":"9 Pattipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap461:1.1":"“Niharante sariramhi, ","tha-ap461:1.2":"vajjamanasu bherisu; ","tha-ap461:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap461:1.4":"pattipupphamapujayim. ","tha-ap461:2.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap461:2.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap461:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap461:2.4":"dehapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap461:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap461:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap461:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap461:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap461:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap461:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap461:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap461:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap461:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap461:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pattipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap461:7.1":"Pattipupphiyattherassapadanam navamam. "}